# Recording Functionality Guidelines

## Alert System

When implementing recording-related alerts:
- Use system background color with rounded corners
- Include clear, concise messages in Japanese
- Provide simple action buttons
- Prevent other interactions during recording

## State Management

Recording state should:
- Be managed through VoiceMemoReducer
- Disable navigation and interaction when recording
- Show appropriate visual feedback
- Handle interruptions gracefully

## UI Feedback

Recording UI must:
- Show clear recording status
- Provide immediate visual feedback
- Use consistent styling with the rest of the app
- Follow iOS design guidelines
